                    <div class="article-icon"><i class="fas fa-random"></i></div>
                    <h3>Diversify Your Income: Side Hustle Fundamentals</h3>
                    <p class="article-brief">How to test a side business without quitting your day job, and the legal/tax basics you need to know.</p>
                    <div class="article-meta">
                        <span><i class="far fa-clock"></i> 9 min read</span>
                        <a href="{{ url('app_page_show', { journey: 'career-capital', slug: 'diversify-income' }) }}" class="read-link">Start <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ===== PHASE 3 – PRACTICAL EXECUTION ===== -->
        <div class="phase-wrapper animate">
            <div class="phase-title">
                <span class="phase-number">3</span>
                <span>Practical Execution · Take real‑world action</span>
            </div>
            <div class="article-grid">
                <div class="article-card">
                    <div class="article-icon"><i class="fas fa-hand-holding-usd"></i></div>
                    <h3>How to Negotiate a Raise or Job Offer (Scripts)</h3>
                    <p class="article-brief">Word‑for‑word scripts and counter‑offer tactics that actually work — based on real recruiter insights.</p>
                    <div class="article-meta">
                        <span><i class="far fa-clock"></i> 12 min read</span>
                        <a href="{{ url('app_page_show', { journey: 'career-capital', slug: 'negotiation-scripts' }) }}" class="read-link">Start <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
