                    <div class="article-icon"><i class="fas fa-globe"></i></div>
                    <h3>Build a Personal Website / Thought Leadership</h3>
                    <p class="article-brief">Step‑by‑step guide to creating a simple site, writing articles or making content that positions you as an authority.</p>
                    <div class="article-meta">
                        <span><i class="far fa-clock"></i> 11 min read</span>
                        <a href="{{ url('app_page_show', { journey: 'career-capital', slug: 'personal-website' }) }}" class="read-link">Start <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="article-card">
                    <div class="article-icon"><i class="fas fa-certificate"></i></div>
                    <h3>Certifications vs. Experience: What Moves the Needle?</h3>
                    <p class="article-brief">Evaluate which credentials actually boost income in your field, and how to signal competence without wasting money.</p>
                    <div class="article-meta">
                        <span><i class="far fa-clock"></i> 8 min read</span>
